            <h1 style="text-align: center; margin: 1px;"><span style="font-family: arial; color: #20288c;">Welcome to Cypress Auto Center Online!</span></h1>
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin: 1px;"><span style="font-family: arial; color: #20288c;">Used Diesel Pickups and Used Diesel Trucks</span></h2>
            <p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: arial; color: #20288c;">We are Northern California's largest reseller of Quality Diesel Pickups and Diesel Trucks.&nbsp; In addition our "Wholesale to the Public" department offers all types of vehicles at huge savings.&nbsp; We are located close to Sacramento, on I-80 about 30 min. from Sacramento in the town of Auburn.</span></p>
            <p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;">&nbsp;</p>
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin: 1px;"><span style="font-family: arial; color: #20288c;">Pre-Owned Diesel Pickups and Pre-Owned Diesel Trucks</span></h2>
            <p><span style="font-family: arial; color: #20288c;">We have "QUALITY VEHICLES", because we purchase the majority of our vehicles from bank sales.&nbsp; Most bank sale vehicles are one owner private and corporate lease returns.&nbsp; As a result you'll find extremely nice trucks and cars in our inventory.&nbsp; Our service department inspects all the major systems to insure good working order.&nbsp; They then recondition and service needed items prior to sale.&nbsp; The service department does not accept work from the general public; however we do work for our customers.&nbsp; The hourly rate for our customers are about half of what some new car dealers charge, and we also give our customers a discount on the parts.&nbsp; In addition, our customers are welcome to have us buy for them thru our vendors.&nbsp; Saving them money on items such as tires, auto glass, paint and body work, upholstery, etc.&nbsp; We strive to have a long term relationship with our customers by providing an excellent product, exceptional service, and fair pricing.</span>&nbsp;</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

	function CheckActive() {

			$("#FooterBar-Wrapper a.ilink.text").addClass("minus").removeClass("plus");

	}

	function OpenDrawer(link, drawer, location) {
		var active = CheckActive();

		if (active == drawer) {
			$("#FooterBar-Drawers").attr("drawer", "none");
			CheckActive();
			//$("#FooterBar-Wrapper a.")
			CloseDrawer(drawer);
			return;
		}
		else if (active != "none") {
			CloseDrawer(active);
			setTimeout(function () {
				$("#FooterBar-Drawers").attr("drawer", drawer);
				CheckActive();
				$("#FooterBar-Drawers div.drawer." + drawer).show();
				$("#FooterBar-Drawers").animate({
					bottom: location
				}, 500, "swing");

			}, 500);
		}
		else {
			$("#FooterBar-Drawers").attr("drawer", drawer);
			CheckActive();
			$("#FooterBar-Drawers div.drawer." + drawer).show();
			$("#FooterBar-Drawers").animate({
				bottom: location
			}, 500, "swing");
		}
	}
	function CloseDrawer(drawer, toopen) {
		$("#FooterBar-Drawers").animate({
			bottom: "-500px"
		}, 500, "swing", function () {
			$("#FooterBar-Drawers .drawer." + drawer).hide();
		});
	}

</script>

function validateEmail(email) { 
  var re = /^(([^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+(\.[^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+)*)|(\".+\"))@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\])|(([a-zA-Z\-0-9]+\.)+[a-zA-Z]{2,}))$/;        
  return re.test(email);
} 

function createCookie(name, value, days) {
  if (days) {
    var date = new Date();
    date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
    var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
  }
  else var expires = "";
  document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
}

function getCookie(c_name) {
  if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
    c_start = document.cookie.indexOf(c_name + "=");
    if (c_start != -1) {
      c_start = c_start + c_name.length + 1;
      c_end = document.cookie.indexOf(";", c_start);
      if (c_end == -1) {
        c_end = document.cookie.length;
      }
      return unescape(document.cookie.substring(c_start, c_end));
    }
  }
  return "";
}
